#509
Name        The Game of Seven Room~
Descr
In this room you can play the game of seven, well...  Only if the
croupier is awake...  The rooms is filled with noise as people gamble their
whole life savings.  Most of them are losing, but not you...  You have luck
with you.  Or at least so you think.  A sign is here.  
~
Flags       indoors~
Sector      inside~
Regen       100 100
ExtraDescr  sign~
SEVEN is a simple dice game.  You place a BET with a choice of under,
seven, or over.  The dealer then rolls two dice, and their values are added
up.  If the result is 8 or greater, it is an "Over", and if the resut is 6
or less, it is a "Under".  If, however, the result is seven, it is a "Seven"
and those who bet on it win back 5 times their wager!  
~
Reset       M 502 1 100
Door        west~ ~ 0 504
~
~
End

#510
Name        The Upper Lower Triple Room~
Descr
Here you are, ready to play a nice game of upper-lower-triple.  What are
you waiting for?  The croupier seems to be willing enough to take you
money...  Why don't you hand it over to him?  A sign is here.  
~
Flags       indoors~
Sector      inside~
Regen       100 100
ExtraDescr  sign~
UPPER-LOWER-TRIPLE is a simple dice game.  You place a BET with a choice
of upper, lower, or triple.  The dealer then rolls three dice, and their
values are added up.  If the result is 11 or greater, it is an "Upper", and
if the resut is 10 or less, it is a "Lower".  If, however, all three dice
show the same numbers, it is a "Triple" and those who bet on it win back 36
times their wager!  
~
Reset       M 500 1 100
Door        south~ ~ 0 504
~
~
End

