all.  You don't even have to say a thing.  Just place your bet and the
croupier will know what do with your money... He looks kind of dodgy and you
remember that sign on the closed down circus games booths.  A sign is here. 
~
Flags       indoors~
Sector      inside~
Regen       100 100
ExtraDescr  sign~
HIGH-DICE is the simplest dice game.  You place a BET.  The dealer then
rolls two dice for the player and then two dice for himself.  If the
player's total is higher the player wins, otherwise he loses.  
~
